              "title": "Former Australian of the Year Richard Scolyer's 'final farewell'",
              "content": {
                "descriptor": {
                  "type": "tagname",
                  "key": "div",
                  "props": {},
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "tagname",
                      "key": "@@standfirst",
                      "props": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "content": "Professor Scolyer wrote he \"would be delighted and humbled to be remembered as a proud everyday Aussie who 'gave it a crack', and in doing so, inspired others to pursue their dreams and passions with humility, love and compassion\"."
